{% comment %}
  Scrolling logo/text marquee strip.
  Parameters: label (optional heading above bar)
  Call individual items by rendering this snippet multiple times, OR use the
  section-level logo-marquee HTML directly for static hardcoded logos.
  This snippet renders the outer wrapper; inner content is passed via capture.
  Usage (static):
    <div class="logo-marquee">
      {% if label != blank %}<p class="logo-marquee__label">{{ label }}</p>{% endif %}
      <div class="logo-marquee__track">
        <div class="logo-marquee__item logo-marquee__item--text">Vidveer</div>
        <div class="logo-marquee__item logo-marquee__item--text">Lassus Tandartsen</div>
        ... (duplicated for loop)
      </div>
    </div>
{% endcomment %}
